    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，时间格式用X表示毫秒或秒都可以，显示格式用%s。P1对应Infra_RedisCache，执行时间最长，从0开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "0",
        "5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，P1在CPU段从0到5执行，标记为active状态。那P1结束后应该触发I/O操作对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "cpu1",
        "0",
        "5",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，P1的I/O操作P1_IO也是访问RedisCache，从第5秒开始，持续2秒到第7秒。这个I/O要标记为关键路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1_IO",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "5",
        "7",
        "crit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P1_IO已添加，crit标记表示关键I/O。接下来P4应该进入CPU，它关联的是Infra_WorkerNode，执行时间比较短。",
      "elements_involved": [
